{"data":[{"name":"90:1","price":"मैं इस नगर (मक्का) की क़सम खाता हूँ!","arabic":"لَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِهَٰذَا ٱلۡبَلَدِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6024,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"lā uq'simu bihādhā al-baladi ","translations":["Nay","I swear","by this","city","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","uq'simu","bihādhā","al-baladi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2640],[2,2640,3510],[3,3510,4350],[4,4350,5685]]}},{"name":"90:2","price":"तथा तुम्हारे लिए इस नगर में लड़ाई हलाल होने वाली है।","arabic":"وَأَنتَ حِلُّۢ بِهَٰذَا ٱلۡبَلَدِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6025,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-anta ḥillun bihādhā al-baladi ","translations":["And you","(are) free (to dwell)","in this","city","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-anta","ḥillun","bihādhā","al-baladi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1740],[2,1740,3370],[3,3370,4260],[4,4260,5635]]}},{"name":"90:3","price":"तथा क़सम है पिता तथा उसकी संतान की!","arabic":"وَوَالِدٖ وَمَا وَلَدَ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6026,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wawālidin wamā walada ","translations":["And the begetter","and what","he begot","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wawālidin","wamā","walada",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1990],[2,1990,2550],[3,2550,3725]]}},{"name":"90:4","price":"निःसंदेह हमने मनुष्य को बड़ी कठिनाई में पैदा किया है।","arabic":"لَقَدۡ خَلَقۡنَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ فِي كَبَدٍ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6027,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"laqad khalaqnā al-insāna fī kabadin ","translations":["Certainly","We have created","man","(to be) in","hardship","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["laqad","khalaqnā","al-insāna","fī","kabadin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,1480],[3,1480,3680],[4,3680,4130],[5,4130,5275]]}},{"name":"90:5","price":"क्या वह समझता है कि उसपर कभी किसी का वश नहीं चलेगा?[1]","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ أَن لَّن يَقۡدِرَ عَلَيۡهِ أَحَدٞ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6028,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1. (1-5) इन आयतों में सर्व प्रथम मक्का नगर में नबी सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम पर जो घटनाएँ घट रही थीं, और आप तथा आपके अनुयायियों को सताया जा रहा था, उसको साक्षी के रूप में प्रस्तुत किया गया है कि इनसान की पैदाइश (रचना) संसार का स्वाद लेने के लिए नहीं हुई है। संसार परिश्रम तथा पीड़ाएँ झेलने का स्थान है। कोई इनसान इस स्थिति से गुज़रे बिना नहीं रह सकता। \"पिता\" से अभिप्राय आदम अलैहिस्सलमा और \"संतान\" से अभिप्राय समस्त मानवजाति (इनसान) हैं। फिर इनसान के इस भ्रम को दूर किया है कि उसके ऊपर कोई शक्ति नहीं है, जो उसके कर्मों को देख रही है, और समय आने पर उसकी पकड़ करेगी।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaḥsabu an lan yaqdira ʿalayhi aḥadun ","translations":["Does he think","that","not","has power","over him","anyone","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaḥsabu","an","lan","yaqdira","ʿalayhi","aḥadun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,980],[2,980,1210],[3,1210,2340],[4,2340,3480],[5,3480,4320],[6,4320,5425]]}},{"name":"90:6","price":"वह कहता है कि मैंने ढेर सारा धन ख़र्च कर दिया।","arabic":"يَقُولُ أَهۡلَكۡتُ مَالٗا لُّبَدًا","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6029,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"yaqūlu ahlaktu mālan lubadan ","translations":["He will say","I have squandered","wealth","abundant","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yaqūlu","ahlaktu","mālan","lubadan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,1940],[3,1940,2600],[4,2600,3835]]}},{"name":"90:7","price":"क्या वह समझता है कि उसे किसी ने नहीं देखा?[2]","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ أَن لَّمۡ يَرَهُۥٓ أَحَدٌ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6030,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2. (1-5) इनमें यह बताया गया है कि संसार में बड़ाई तथा प्रधानता के ग़लत पैमाने बना लिए गए हैं, और जो दिखावे के लिए धन व्यय (ख़र्च) करता है उसकी प्रशंसा की जाती है, जबकि उसके ऊपर एक शक्ति है जो यह देख रही है कि उसने किन राहों में और किस लिए धन ख़र्च किया है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaḥsabu an lam yarahu aḥadun ","translations":["Does he think","that","not","sees him","anyone","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaḥsabu","an","lam","yarahu","aḥadun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,1210],[3,1210,1840],[4,1840,4140],[5,4140,5265]]}},{"name":"90:8","price":"क्या हमने उसके लिए दो आँखें नहीं बनाईं?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَل لَّهُۥ عَيۡنَيۡنِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6031,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alam najʿal lahu ʿaynayni ","translations":["Have not","We made","for him","two eyes","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","najʿal","lahu","ʿaynayni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1420],[3,1420,2020],[4,2020,5505]]}},{"name":"90:9","price":"तथा एक ज़बान और दो होंठ (नहीं बनाए)?","arabic":"وَلِسَانٗا وَشَفَتَيۡنِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6032,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"walisānan washafatayni ","translations":["And a tongue","and two lips","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["walisānan","washafatayni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2210],[2,2210,5825]]}},{"name":"90:10","price":"और हमने उसे दोनों मार्ग दिखा दिए?!","arabic":"وَهَدَيۡنَٰهُ ٱلنَّجۡدَيۡنِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6033,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wahadaynāhu al-najdayni ","translations":["And shown him","the two ways","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wahadaynāhu","al-najdayni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1480],[2,1480,5865]]}},{"name":"90:11","price":"परंतु उसने दुर्लभ घाटी में प्रवेश ही नहीं किया।","arabic":"فَلَا ٱقۡتَحَمَ ٱلۡعَقَبَةَ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6034,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"falā iq'taḥama al-ʿaqabata ","translations":["But not","he has attempted","the steep path","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["falā","iq'taḥama","al-ʿaqabata",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,360],[2,360,1210],[3,1210,2735]]}},{"name":"90:12","price":"और तुम्हें किस चीज़ ने ज्ञात कराया कि वह दुर्लभ 'घाटी' क्या है?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡعَقَبَةُ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6035,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā al-ʿaqabatu ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","the steep path (is)","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","al-ʿaqabatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2150],[2,2150,3200],[3,3200,3370],[4,3370,4855]]}},{"name":"90:13","price":"(वह) गर्दन छुड़ाना है।","arabic":"فَكُّ رَقَبَةٍ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6036,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fakku raqabatin ","translations":["(It is) freeing","a neck","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fakku","raqabatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1915]]}},{"name":"90:14","price":"या किसी भूख वाले दिन में खाना खिलाना है।","arabic":"أَوۡ إِطۡعَٰمٞ فِي يَوۡمٖ ذِي مَسۡغَبَةٖ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6037,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"aw iṭ'ʿāmun fī yawmin dhī masghabatin ","translations":["Or","feeding","in","a day","of","severe hunger","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["aw","iṭ'ʿāmun","fī","yawmin","dhī","masghabatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,2280],[3,2280,2820],[4,2820,4340],[5,4340,4790],[6,4790,6195]]}},{"name":"90:15","price":"किसी रिश्तेदार अनाथ को।","arabic":"يَتِيمٗا ذَا مَقۡرَبَةٍ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6038,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"yatīman dhā maqrabatin ","translations":["An orphan","of","near relationship","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["yatīman","dhā","maqrabatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1660],[2,1660,2130],[3,2130,3595]]}},{"name":"90:16","price":"या मिट्टी में लथड़े हुए निर्धन को।[3]","arabic":"أَوۡ مِسۡكِينٗا ذَا مَتۡرَبَةٖ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6039,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3. (8-16) इन आयतों में फरमाया गया है कि इनसान को ज्ञान और चिंतन के साधन और योग्यताएँ देकर हमने उसके सामने भलाई तथा बुराई के दोनों मार्ग खोल दिए हैं, एक नैतिक पतन की ओर ले जाता है और उसमें मन को अति स्वाद मिलता है। दूसरा नैतिक ऊँचाईयों की राह जिस में कठिनाईयाँ हैं। और उसी को घाटी कहा गया है। जिसमें प्रवेश करने वालों के कर्तव्य में है कि दासों को मुक्त करें, निर्धनों को भोजन कराएँ इत्यादि, वही लोग स्वर्गवासी हैं। और वे जिन्होंने अल्लाह की आयतों का इनकार किया, वे नरकवासी हैं। आयत संख्या 17 का अर्थ यह है कि सत्य विश्वास (ईमान) के बिना कोई सत्कर्म मान्य नहीं है। इसमें सुखी समाज की विशेषता भी बताई गई है कि दूसरे को सहनशीलता तथा दया का उपदेश दिया जाए और अल्लाह पर सत्य विश्वास रखा जाए।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"aw mis'kīnan dhā matrabatin ","translations":["Or","a needy person","in","misery","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["aw","mis'kīnan","dhā","matrabatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,2500],[3,2500,2960],[4,2960,4475]]}},{"name":"90:17","price":"फिर वह उन लोगों में से हो, जो ईमान लाए और एक-दूसरे को धैर्य रखने की सलाह दी और एक-दूसरे को दया करने की सलाह दी।","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَانَ مِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَتَوَاصَوۡاْ بِٱلصَّبۡرِ وَتَوَاصَوۡاْ بِٱلۡمَرۡحَمَةِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6040,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma kāna mina alladhīna āmanū watawāṣaw bil-ṣabri watawāṣaw bil-marḥamati ","translations":["Then","he is","of","those who","believe","and enjoin (each other)","to patience","and enjoin (each other)","to compassion","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","kāna","mina","alladhīna","āmanū","watawāṣaw","bil-ṣabri","watawāṣaw","bil-marḥamati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,1710],[3,1710,2140],[4,2140,3290],[5,3290,4480],[6,4480,5740],[7,5740,6790],[8,6790,8120],[9,8120,10175]]}},{"name":"90:18","price":"यही लोग दाहिने हाथ वाले (सौभाग्यशाली) हैं।","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6041,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ulāika aṣḥābu al-maymanati ","translations":["Those","(are the) companions","(of) the right (hand)","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["ulāika","aṣḥābu","al-maymanati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2750],[2,2750,3770],[3,3770,5675]]}},{"name":"90:19","price":"और जिन लोगों ने हमारी आयतों का इनकार किया, वही लोग बाएँ हाथ वाले (दुर्भाग्यशाली) हैं।","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا هُمۡ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6042,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna kafarū biāyātinā hum aṣḥābu al-mashamati ","translations":["But those who","disbelieve","in Our Verses","they","(are the) companions","(of) the left (hand)","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","kafarū","biāyātinā","hum","aṣḥābu","al-mashamati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,2120],[3,2120,3890],[4,3890,4330],[5,4330,5330],[6,5330,7175]]}},{"name":"90:20","price":"उनपर (हर ओर से) बंद की हुई आग होगी।","arabic":"عَلَيۡهِمۡ نَارٞ مُّؤۡصَدَةُۢ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6043,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalayhim nārun mu'ṣadatun ","translations":["Over them","(will be the) Fire","closed in","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalayhim","nārun","mu'ṣadatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1910],[3,1910,5505]]}}],"chapter":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad","Chapter Al-Balad","Balad","Surah Balad","Chapter Balad","Al Balad","Surah Al Balad","Chapter Al Balad","Surah 90","Chapter 90","The City","البلد"],"version":{"k